goyo.vim (고요)
===============

Distraction-free writing in Vim.

Project Home: https://github.com/junegunn/goyo.vim
Screenshot: https://raw.github.com/junegunn/i/master/goyo.png

Usage
-----

:Goyo [width]

Configuration
-------------

- g:goyo_width (default: 80)
- g:goyo_margin_top (default: 4)
- g:goyo_margin_bottom (default: 4)
